# Premium UI/UX Upgrade — Jetski AI Code Reviewer

Transform the existing functional frontend into a world-class SaaS developer platform while preserving 100% backend compatibility.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Zero backend changes.** All upgrades are purely UI/UX. Every existing React Query hook, Socket.IO listener, Axios call, auth flow, and route remains untouched.

---

## Scope & Constraints

- **DO NOT** modify: `services/`, `providers/`, feature `.service.ts` files, `types.ts` files, or routing structure
- **DO NOT** change any `useMutation`, `useQuery`, Socket.IO event handlers, or auth logic
- **ONLY** upgrade the visual layer: components, styles, animations, and new UI-only features

